      "text": "そして研究熱心だ。新人の大会であっても\n勉強を欠かさない。トップにいる者とはそういう者だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ they’re study-holics. This may be a competition for newcomers‚\nbut they’re still doing their homework. That’s what it means to be at the top.",
